# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

Wordle 

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

Wordle: A game that takes a random word that the user will guess. It will say what letters are wrong or in the wrong place and vice versa.

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

My game will randomize a word that the user will have to guess. The user will type in a five letter word. The game will indicate what letters are wrong, what letters are right but in the wrong place, and what letters are right and in the right place. The features it will have are different colors to indicate the different levels. When the user finally gets the word right, the word will be all green. 
